{"about_the_game":"<strong>Once upon a time... ...STONE.</strong><br><br><strong>A STONE</strong> cannot move by itself.<br><br>In fact, we cannot tell whether the <strong>STONE</strong> has the will to go up or not.<br>But we raise the <strong>STONE</strong> to the sky. That's because it's a <strong>game</strong>.<br><br><strong>Impossible Stone Game</strong> presents a new type of platform game.<br>You move the stone by applying shock waves with bombs to the stone that cannot move.<br><br>There are various obstacles on the rainbow-colored journey of the stone to the sky.<br>Beautiful but annoying obstacles that appear according to each theme will try to block the journey.<br>What kind of reward will the stone receive when it overcomes adversity through numerous falls?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A 2D platform game with a completely new control method.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Simple and easy to understand, but challenging and difficult gameplay.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Minimal level design with various themes that are tightly woven.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>8-bit retro graphic design and fun chiptune music that matches the design.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"start on RED","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3149970/cd17c2218a00c059578dcce05b20af498a2a1bda.jpg"},{"name":"annoying ORANGE","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3149970/246dc55ae1457d332fa67c28bd7523b3ac317dcd.jpg"},{"name":"YELLOW crane tower","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3149970/09aede3d0d3dc3e813170c23039d7c29c578842f.jpg"},{"name":"stop on GREEN","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3149970/a0bc1b962c2a511cbcb5012bbc72e55ce3f0bd51.jpg"},{"name":"russian BLUE","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3149970/4ca9921fc200c19